{"tid":1627582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 天水圍翠湖輕鐵站附近大量黑警","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:54:22.000Z","uid":149923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"55ba31d44ad21650240d0bcd72de05ad5c529deb","tid":1627582,"uid":149923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:33:41.000Z","msg":"一開頭剩係有警車同狗私家車停係路邊<br />\n之後有手足開始嗌口號 黑警 叫滾 走之類既<br />\n一開始黑警並冇舉動<br />\n過左一陣開始係架私家車度照樓上平台既手足<br />\n包括經過既市民<br />\n過左陣一大派落車追捕係路邊叫既手足<br />\n更包圍屋苑附近出入口(輕鐵站嗰邊 同近銀座嗰邊既出入口)<br />\n有居民圍觀黑警被黑警斥罵 &ldquo;冇咩嘢就翻上樓&rdquo;<br />\n天水圍手足小心<br />\n附圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxz5UT0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgxz5UT0.jpg&h=3e57be18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTiB1y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTiB1y3.jpg&h=a8e857b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7554532da861d5567148662c2c318683055c932b","tid":1627582,"uid":133655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96709e312f44dd798831e793cf4dfcf8b0d81fb4","tid":1627582,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"裝修新手入一入黎 仲有召喚ust南亞仔同南亞手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627570</a>"},{"pid":"ed3bdb2dc090ffbd2b417c94072bcdd27cfffcbf","tid":1627582,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"班狗係鍾意出黎搞事俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e737afaddb04ce651ce653d22be958ceb03f535b","tid":1627582,"uid":26812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩好齊心一齊扮狗叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270a521025e08dc37d866bef4a81b2feebf019eb","tid":1627582,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite